data.title: Famous Libra Models
data.meta_description: This list of famous Libra models includes Kim Kardashian, Dakota Johnson, Katie Piper, Maddie Ziegler, Monica Bellucci and many more.
data.text:
1

Bella Hadid

(American Model Known for Her 27-Appearances on 'Vogue' Magazine Covers)

123

49

Birthdate: October 9, 1996

Birthplace: Washington, D.C., United States

One of the most popular American models of the current generation, Bella Hadid has been featured in popular magazines, such as Vogue and Harper's Bazaar. She was voted Model of the Year in 2016 by industry professionals. The same year, Hadid contributed to Johny Dar's Jeans for Refugees project in order to raise fund for the International Rescue Committee.

2

Candice Swanepoel

(South African Model and Victoria's Secret Angel)

77

19

Birthdate: October 20, 1988

Birthplace: Mooi River, South Africa

Candice Swanepoel is a South African model known for her association with Victoria's Secret. In 2016, Swanepoel was ranked eighth among the top-earning models, according to Forbes. Also known for her charity work, Swanepoel works closely with mothers2mothers, a nonprofit organization that aims at averting mother-to-child transmission of HIV by providing support and education for pregnant women living with HIV.

(Fashion Model)

56

Hungarian model Barbara Palvin gained fame after appearing in the 2016 Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue. She was later named a Victoria's Secret Angel. She has modeled for top-notch brands such as Prada and Chanel. She was also seen as Greek mythological figure Antimache in the 2014 film Hercules.
